title: The Dave & Drake Show
description: It's our LAST LIVE show of 2021! And to send us off Dave & Drake had tons of Dirt to talk about, Finish The Lyrics for Bieber Tickets, We went back a re-listened to some old school bits that Dave did back in the day, Why will your Christmas be special this year?, Talked to Johnathon Fogel, Gave away Vikings tickets, Are these people swingers for doing this?, & More!
